Butler Network!

328
00:23:33,850 --> 00:23:35,880
Hello. I'm Katsura Hinagiku.

329
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:38,230
How did you all like this week's Hayate no Gotoku?

330
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:41,030
It was an episode where I had the most lines to say.

331
